What is Django?
- Python web framework 
- Python server side framework 
- Design to get you start fast 
- Batteries included (It is heavy weight framework as it have pre-included packages)
- MVT(Model view Template) Design pattern


What is web framework?
- Collection of modules, packages and libraires, Designed to speed up development

Building API's in django?
django + django rest framework

Other python framework?
- FastAPI
- Flask 
- CheeryPi
